      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude98 Affordable & Gets the Job Done! \u2014 Here's a practical opportunity for budget-conscious buyers! This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but we want to be upfront that it shows its age with some visible wear, minor cosmetic imperfections, and likely a few maintenance items that could use attention down the road. It's not a showstopper, but it's a real, functional vehicle at an honest price. Great for someone who needs reliable transportation and doesn't mind a little TLC!",
