      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride that gets the job done without the premium price tag? This car might be your answer! It's in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives dependably, though you'll notice some visible wear on the exterior and interior that comes with its age and mileage. No frills, no fuss \u2014 just honest, functional transportation at a price that makes sense. Come take it for a spin and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 18000.0,
